headline: Workday to acquire AI firm Sana for $1.1 billion
summary: (Reuters) -     Workday (WDAY) said on Tuesday it would acquire artificial intelligence firm Sana for about $1.1 billion, as the human resources software provider looks to drive demand by integrating AI capabilities into its products.
